page.title: 12Food in 1985,Bitteswell
page.content: This is a list that four third year boys made from the food they have eaten in 1985: Chicken,barbecued sardines,seafood salad,Chilli Con Carne,Baked Beans, cauliflower,Big Mac Hamburgers,beef, lamb,pork,pizza,potatoes,sweet corn, fruit,sausages,carrots,salami, Spaghetti Bolognes,Lancashire Hot Pot, cereals,chips,pasta,cobs,prawns,chops, smoked salmon,smoked mackerel,curry and rice,eggs,ham,corned beef,onion, dumplings,Shepherds Pie,mushy peas, toasted sandwiches,mushrooms,bread, cabbage,Sunday Lunch,Lasagne, bacon, crisps,Cheesey Criss Cross snack, biscuits,Peanut Butter,Meat Spread, spam,cheese-on-toast,peas,colslaw, lobster,Cordon Bleu,Mexican food, cockles,crabs and mussels.
